snippet.title: Official The Last Dimension Trailer
snippet.description:
Play through challenging levels with unique soundtracks! How far can you get?
Do not touch the fractals and do not stay in the black void to reach higher dimensions! Every level has its own, endless fractals, so what are you waiting for? 

Visit seismic.at
http://seismic.at/

Download The Last Dimension
https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=at.sectorinfinity.lastdimension
